package com.example.androidexample
  • Class
    Description
    Chat
    Chat activity that handles communication with the WebSocket server and displays messages in a chat interface.
    ChatRoom1
    ChatRoom1 activity that handles communication with the WebSocket server for chatroom 1 and displays messages in a chat interface.
    ChatRoom2
    ChatRoom2 activity that handles communication with the WebSocket server for chatroom 2 and displays messages in a chat interface.
    ChatRoom3
    ChatRoom3 activity that handles communication with the WebSocket server for chatroom 3 and displays messages in a chat interface.
    GameOver
    GameOver activity that displays the final score after the game ends and updates the user's game statistics on the server.
    Leaderboard
    Class to see leaderboard of all users and their total score
    LoginActivity
    Class to log in to our app.
    MainActivity
    This is the first view upon opening the app.
    PlayActivity
    PlayActivity that handles the game logic, including displaying panoramic images, interacting with a map to select locations, and calculating scores.
    SignupActivity
    Class for user to create an account
    Stats
    Class to view users stats
    UserHome
    The homescreen the user sees after logging into an account
    UserProfileActivity
    View to see profile information
    WebSocketListener
    Interface defining methods for handling WebSocket events.
    WebSocketManager
    Singleton WebSocketManager instance used for managing WebSocket connections in the Android application.
